---
title: Double Honey Haloumi & Pesto Kumato Salad with Avocado & Garlic Chilli Croutons
description: We've teamed up with Perfection Fresh, to bring you some superstar ingredients to level up your next meal. These super sweet, yet super versatile tomato variety carries the perfect sweetness ratio to level up any dish. When paired with honey haloumi and a rainbow salad, these tomatoes will have you savouring each and every bite. Compliments to the Kumato we say!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y25_R1043_W43_AU_R46491-3_Main_high-984ad63e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com.au/recipecards/card/688957f6b6ffa7a20c3bead2-en-AU.pdf
